com.inqwell.any

Interface ByteI

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Any, Serializable, Value
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AnyByte, ConstByte, ConstByteDecor, NativeDescriptor.EnumByte

    public interface ByteI
extends Value
    The integer value type interface. Concrete implementations are the mutable and const classes and the const decorator for use when constness is required to be dynamic.
